HONG KONG , November 29 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- The Chinese People 's Liberation Army -LRB- PLA -RRB- Hong Kong Garrison will send a vessel and a helicopter to take part in a search and rescue drill for air accidents , which is organized by the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region -LRB- SAR -RRB- from November 30 to December 3 .
In accordance with the Basic Law , the PLA Hong Kong Garrison will participate in the drill at the request of the Hong Kong SAR government and its participation has got the approval of the higher authorities , PLA Garrison spokesman Feng Wei said .
He said the purpose of the PLA Garrison troops ' participation in the drill is to familiarize themselves with the sea area and air space concerned , enhance contact and coordination with the SAR government and concerned organizations , so as to help the SAR government in rescue operations in accordance with the Basic Law and the Garrison Law when the need arises .
